ActBudget Implementation Act, 2017, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing July 29, 2019 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) July 29, 2019, as the day on which subsections 318(1), 320(1) and 322(1), section 323, subsections 324(2) and 325(1) and (2), sections 326 to 328, subsections 329(1) and (2), sections 330 to 337, subsection 338(1), sections 339 to 349 and 351 to 355, subsections 356(2) and (3), 363(8) and 364(2), section 365, subsection 368(1) and sections 370, 378 to 383, 387 and 391 to 397 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2017, NO. 1, chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada 2017 COME INTO FORCE; and (2) fixing July 29, 2019, as the day on which subsection 318(2), section 319, subsections 338(2) and 356(1) and section 384 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2017, NO. 1 COME INTO FORCE.
